Sentencas: Series of proton-blocking La2NiO4+delta (LNO)-LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3-delta (LNF) (1:0, 7:3, 5:5, 3:7, 0:1 wt.%) composites were evaluated as cathodes for BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-delta (BZCY)-based proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cell (H-SOFC).
Titulo: A new cobalt-free proton-blocking composite cathode La2NiO4+δ-LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3-δ for BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ-based solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The X-ray diffraction (XRD) results show a good chemical compatibility for each composition below 1100 degrees C. Electrochemical studies reveal that LNO-LNF73 shows the lowest area specific polarization resistance in symmetrical cells and the best electrochemical performance in single cell tests with the highest maximum power density (MPD) and the lowest interfacial polarization resistance (R-p).
Titulo: A new cobalt-free proton-blocking composite cathode La2NiO4+δ-LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3-δ for BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ-based solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: These results corroborate the electrical conductivity analysis.
Titulo: A new cobalt-free proton-blocking composite cathode La2NiO4+δ-LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3-δ for BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ-based solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The single cell with LNO-LNF73 as cathode outputs the MPD of 590 mW cm(-2) and the R-p of 0.091 Omega cm(2) at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: A new cobalt-free proton-blocking composite cathode La2NiO4+δ-LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3-δ for BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ-based solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This work confirms that LNO-LNF73 composite material could be a promising cathode for H-SOFC.
Titulo: A new cobalt-free proton-blocking composite cathode La2NiO4+δ-LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3-δ for BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ-based solid oxide fuel cells
